'''Rann''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Brosi]]. The city was within the area of influence of the [[Brosin Underground]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], around [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]].
